User-Agent:       Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64; rv:2.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/4.0
Build Identifier: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64; rv:2.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/4.0

When trying to print the movie times on Regal Theaters website, I get a first page
that is almost complete and the rest of the pages are blank.  I enter my zip code and then select.  I then hit "print this page" and it should print out all the movie listings.  This does work properly in firefox 3.6.15.

Reproducible: Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1. got to page http://www.regmovies.com/ticketsandshowtimes/
2. enter a zip code and select
3. pick print this page and it will not print properly
Actual Results:  
Prints most of the first page and then a number of blank pages

Expected Results:  
should see a number of pages of movie listings..
